-- Liverpool Manager Kenny Dalglish Leaves Soccer Club, BBC Says
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   E l s e r
-- 2012-05-16T15:30:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-16/liverpool-manager-kenny-dalglish-leaves-soccer-club-bbc-says.html
Liverpool manager  Kenny Dalglish  has
left the English soccer club because of its poor performance in
the Premier League, the British Broadcasting Corp. said today,
without citing anyone.  The 61-year-old Dalglish met with owners John W. Henry and
Tom Werner in Boston earlier this week.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christopher Elser in London at 
 celser@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
